Motivated Seller! ASSUMABLE 4.5% VA LOAN & 3-2-1 Buydown Available 

Introducing the stunning Rosemary plan, nestled in the charming Dawson Creek community at The Waters.
As you step onto the inviting front porch, you are greeted by a glimpse of the open concept kitchen, living, and dining areas. The space is adorned with luxurious Luxury Vinyl Plank (LVP) flooring and boasts high ceilings, creating an atmosphere of elegance and sophistication.
Prepare to be amazed by the cook's kitchen, a true culinary haven. A generously sized work island with bar seating takes center stage, surrounded by an abundance of cabinet space that will cater to all your storage needs. The kitchen also features a walk-in pantry featuring upgraded shelving, quartz countertops, a stylish subway tile backsplash, and designer fixtures, ensuring that it stands out as the heart of the home. The separate dining area is enhanced by carefully selected lighting, adding a touch of charm and warmth to every meal.
The owner's suite offers a private sanctuary, complete with an en-suite bath featuring double vanities and a generously sized walk-in closet, ensuring ample space for all your belongings. Additionally, the main floor includes a guest bedroom and a full bath, perfect for accommodating visitors
Upstairs, you will discover two additional bedrooms, each with its own private bath, as well as a bonus room and a cozy sitting area. This versatile space offers endless possibilities, whether you envision it as a game room, a home theater, or a dedicated office space.
Convenience is key, and this home delivers with a back-entry drop station, providing a designated area to store everyday items. A spacious screened back porch and a two-car carport with storage complete the package.
Don't miss the opportunity to call this exceptional home your own. 

Call today to schedule a showing! This incentive package combined with location is second to none!
